<topic id="how-to-exist">
  <title>Configuring an eXist Database Connection</title>
  <body>
    <p>There are two ways to configure the support for an eXist database:<ul>
        <li>Use the dedicated eXist connection wizard.<ol>
            <li><ph conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/Open-the-preferences-page"/>, go to
                <uicontrol>Data Sources</uicontrol> and click the <uicontrol>Create eXist-db XML
                connection</uicontrol> link.</li>
            <li>Enter your connection details in the connection wizard and click
                <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.<note type="important">To create an eXist connection using
                this wizard, <ph keyref="product"/> expects the
                  <filepath>exist/webstart/exist.jnlp</filepath> path to be accessible at the
                provided <uicontrol>Host</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Port</uicontrol>.</note></li>
            <li>To view your connection, go to the <xref
                href="../topics/relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"
                  ><uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>
              <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view-parenthesis"/> or switch to the
                <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
              <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"><term>perspective</term></xref>.</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol>Data Sources</uicontrol> preferences page to configure your connection.<ol>
            <li><xref href="configure-exist-datasource.dita#configure-exist-datasource">Configure
                eXist <term>Data Source</term> drivers</xref>.</li>
            <li><xref href="configure-exist-connection.dita#configure-exist-connection">Configure an
                eXist <term>Connection</term></xref>.</li>
            <li>To view your connection, go to the <xref
                href="../topics/relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"
                  ><uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>
              <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view-parenthesis"/> or switch to the
                <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
              <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"><term>perspective</term></xref>.</li>
          </ol></li>
      </ul></p>
  </body>
</topic>
